messages.msgSnippet: ... Not so anxious, this is the third time around.  I m just really hoping that this delivery resembles the second (3 fast hours) rather than the first (12
messages.messageBody:
>Thanks for speaking up Kelly!!!! So how are you feeling? Aside from
>anxious??
>Mary B

Not so anxious, this is the third time around. I'm just really hoping that
this delivery resembles the second (3 fast hours) rather than the first (12
long, yucky hours.)

I am just really tired of being tired. Of "feeling pregnant" if that makes
sense. It's just sapping me in ways I forget that it does. I am VERY glad
this is the last time we are doing this.

However, I just put down a down payment on a used minivan (a Town &
Conuntry, very posh) and we'll pick it up next week. Having a car (which we
have only had since May 1 after 4 years with none) is a major change in our
lives and having one that actually will FIT our family, our whole new
family, is a thrill. I'm very excited about that.

NOw if I could just sleep!!! I'ts 4 AM, if anyone noticed the time
tamp. -sigh-

Thanks for asking, Mary.

Kelly
